sequenceDiagram
    participant GUI as GUI/CLI
    participant SSH as RemoteLinuxDataSource
    participant SSHMon as SSHMonitorRaw
    participant Script as linux_monitor_remote.sh
    participant Remote as Remote Linux Host
    participant DB as Remote SQLite DB
    
    GUI->>SSH: connect()
    SSH->>SSHMon: __init__(host, user, password)
    SSHMon->>Remote: ssh user@host
    Remote-->>SSHMon: Connection OK
    
    SSHMon->>Script: Deploy & Execute
    Script->>Remote: Read /proc/stat, /proc/meminfo, etc.
    Remote-->>Script: Raw system data
    Script->>DB: INSERT INTO monitoring_data
    Script-->>SSHMon: JSON stream (stdout)
    
    loop Every 1 second
        SSHMon->>SSHMon: Parse JSON line
        SSHMon->>SSHMon: Buffer in queue (100 samples)
    end
    
    GUI->>SSH: get_cpu_info()
    SSH->>SSHMon: get_latest_data()
    SSHMon-->>SSH: Buffered raw data
    SSH->>SSH: Process raw_data to GUI format
    SSH-->>GUI: {cpu, memory, gpu, ...}
    
    Note over GUI: Display Real-time Data
    
    GUI->>SSH: Export HTML
    SSH->>Remote: Pull /tmp/monitor_tool_user.db
    SSH->>SSH: Query remote DB via SSH
    SSH-->>GUI: Sample data list
    GUI->>GUI: Generate HTML Report